Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.51,0:00:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}Cuando la lluvia de lágrimas cae y toca mis mejillas, es algo hermoso.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Por las estúpidas reglas de las que no pude escapar, lloré.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.21,0:00:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi mapa del futuro era muy borroso.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.63,0:00:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queriendo llenar mi cansado corazón,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.30,0:00:40.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,sólo pude juntar cosas que no necesito.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Le digo adiós a esos queridos días,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.33,0:00:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,porque no regresarán.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.44,0:00:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En la esquina de la noche, silenciosamente,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.82,0:01:01.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mi cerrado corazoncito comienza a abrirse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.62,0:01:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mi color se está tornando en un tono más profundo y suave
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,mientras recibo la luz de la mañana.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.51,0:01:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Cuando la lluvia de lágrimas cae y toca mis mejillas, es algo hermoso.
Comment: 0,0:00:01.01,0:00:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the rain of tears falls down and hits my cheeks, it’s a beautiful thing.
Comment: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unable to step outside the stupid rules, I cried.
Comment: 0,0:00:26.74,0:00:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My map of the future was too blurry.
Comment: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanting to fill up my worn-down heart,
Comment: 0,0:00:36.70,0:00:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just gathered things I didn’t need.
Comment: 0,0:00:41.72,0:00:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye, I say, because those beloved days won’t come back.
Comment: 0,0:00:51.36,0:01:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the corner of the night, quietly, my little closed heart is starting to open up.
Comment: 0,0:01:02.02,0:01:12.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My color is changing to a deeper and gentler shade as I take in the morning light.
Comment: 0,0:01:13.06,0:01:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the rain of tears falls down and hits my cheeks, it’s a beautiful thing.
